    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a poor-condition car. Buyers should expect significant wear and issues throughout. The exterior shows heavy scratches, dents, and paint fading across multiple panels. The interior has considerable wear including torn upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and a worn headliner. Mechanically, this car has known issues that will require attention \u2014 it is best suited for a buyer comfortable with repairs or someone looking for a project vehicle or parts car. It does run and drive, but reliability cannot be guaranteed. Priced accordingly to reflect its current state, this listing is for buyers who understand and accept the condition as described.",
      "price": 4500.0,
