      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable ride or a project car with potential? This vehicle is priced to reflect its current condition \u2014 it has some significant wear and will need attention, but it's an honest opportunity for the right buyer. Whether you're a hands-on mechanic looking for a fixer-upper or just need basic transportation on a tight budget, this could be your ticket. Come take a look and see what's possible \u2014 priced accordingly so you know exactly what you're getting!",
      "price": 6000.0,
