    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 an increasingly rare find in the used-car market. The exterior is virtually flawless, presenting no scratches, dents, paint chips, or blemishes of any kind. The paint retains its full factory depth and luster, and every panel aligns perfectly. The interior is equally pristine \u2014 all surfaces, upholstery, and trim are immaculate, with no staining, cracking, fading, or wear marks to speak of. Every mechanical system functions exactly as intended, with no warning lights, unusual noises, or performance concerns. The tires have excellent tread remaining, and all electronics, climate controls, and safety features operate flawlessly. This is a vehicle you can purchase with full confidence \u2014 it has been genuinely well-cared-for and shows it in every detail. If you're looking for a used car that feels as close to new as possible, this is it.",
      "price": 47000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_10_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_10",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Reliable & Ready to Roll \u2014 Honest Value for Smart Buyers! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in fair condition and delivers exactly what a solid daily driver should \u2014 dependable transportation at a budget-friendly price! It starts right up, drives smoothly, and handles everyday commutes with ease. You'll notice some cosmetic wear consistent with its age, including minor exterior blemishes and interior signs of use, but nothing that affects its road-worthiness. If you're looking for a practical, no-nonsense vehicle without the premium price tag, this one deserves a look! Come see it in person \u2014 we're proud to show it exactly as it is. \ud83d\udd11",
      "price": 19500.0,
