    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed in good condition \u2014 a solid, well-maintained example that offers reliable performance and a presentable appearance without the premium price tag of a mint-condition unit. The exterior shows only minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with normal use, such as light surface scratches and small stone chips, but retains good overall paint integrity with no significant rust, dents, or damage. The interior is clean and functional, with modest wear on high-contact surfaces like the driver's seat and steering wheel, but no tears, major stains, or broken components. Mechanically, the car runs and drives confidently \u2014 all major systems are in good working order, and it has been properly maintained. Buyers can expect a dependable, everyday-ready vehicle that has been cared for, though it is not a showroom-quality piece. A pre-purchase inspection is always welcome and encouraged.",
